### HTTPS for secure connections

Midtrans forces HTTPS for all services using TLS (SSL), including our public website and Merchant Administration Portal.

- `snap.js` is served only over HTTPS, and host in our server (production). We suggest you to do not host snap.js by yourself.

<br>

### Sensitive data Encryption

Midtrans encrypt card number with AES-256. We storing, decrypting and transmitting all sensitive data in separate hosting infrastucture and doesn't share credential with other services (API, website, etc). None of Midtrans server and employee able to obtain plaintext card number.

